{
  "texts": [
    "In the case of point 1, GPT-3.5 managed to extract more detailed information, identifying both 'non-oriented PMMA layer' and 'oriented PMMA layer' instead of merely labeling it as 'PMMA'.",
    "Neither GPT-3.5 nor Materi-alsBERT were successful in extracting any bandgap data for points 2 and 3, respectively.",
    "With regard to point 4, GPT-3.5 incorrectly identified the thermal decomposition temperature as the Tg value.",
    "Meanwhile, Materi-alsBERT was unable to extract the high bandgap value.",
    "Points 5 and 6 were identified as a composite and blend, respectively."
